1. *Borimo* se za pravdu! (We are fighting for justice!)
2. Oni *bore* se za svoja prava. (They are fighting for their rights.)
3. Mi *borimo* se za našu budućnost. (We are fighting for our future.)
4. Oni *borili* su se za svoje vrednosti. (They were fighting for their values.)
5. Mi ćemo *boriti* se za bolje sutra. (We will fight for a better tomorrow.)